Scripted button. Custom widget intended for movement or repositioning of other controls within a stack.

The button is grouped with 2 fields for demonstration. Movement/repositioning of the controls is done in the mouseUp handler. Edit this handler to move your own controls.

The button references 4 images. The ids for these images are stored in the following custom properties set on the button:

cMoveUpIcon
cMoveUpHiliteIcon
cMoveDownHiliteIcon
cMoveDownIcon

Note that this control requires the "Revolution Icons" image library to be tranferred to your stack using Distribution Builder when you are preparing your stack for distribution.